{
  "schema": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "data": {"type": "array"}
    },
    "required": ["data"]
  },
  "data": "https://api.example.com/data",
  "options": {}
}
</tool_call>

Now I'll save the validated data to a file using the file writer tool. Since the task requires parsing into an unspecified format, I'll use the default JSON format. I'll use the validated data from the previous step as input.

